{"tid":508822,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇發覺而家啲細路越嚟越唔識尊重人？","createTime":"2017-12-24T15:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-24T16:00:49.000Z","uid":106336,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"291767c65a620c25f55b987a9431764acb51ca1f","tid":508822,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T15:35:27.000Z","msg":"是咁啲，今晚同老豆食完飯搭車返屋企<br />\n一上到上層就聽到成班細路好嘈，隔籬坐咗個佢哋識嘅男士，之後佢哋落車先知，好似係啲社區中心幾個大人帶住啲細路咁。<br />\n點知嗰班細路不斷尖叫，又係到講咩屎尿屁，講晒粗口咁，<br />\n但係坐係佢哋隔籬識嗰個男士完全冇諗過阻止佢哋，<br />\n終於我忍唔住同個男人話「唔好意思，可唔可以靜少少」。<br />\n結果班細路淨係喺度好小學雞咁話「你先係最嘈呀」之裏嘅説話<br />\n個男士又冇諗過話好認真咁叫佢哋細聲啲咁<br />\n我明每個人講嘢都有自由，細路嘈都正常，但係真係唔好咁騷擾人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n同埋呢啲所謂社區中心嘅職員有冇諗過班細路真係好冇禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c37576ebef32103d7399fb2e533f3b94b64aa1","tid":508822,"uid":48286,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T15:45:10.000Z","msg":"每一代人都會屌下一代人"},{"pid":"72fc1f674d8e776cf11550aa1f08ce683ec601f2","tid":508822,"uid":106336,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a6c37576ebef32103d7399fb2e533f3b94b64aa1","tid":508822,"uid":48286,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T15:45:10.000Z","msg":"每一代人都會屌下一代人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T15:49:40.000Z","msg":"我只係想佢哋靜少少啫 好過分咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a3fda12ed960cef392cf7a74c901b189a42084","tid":508822,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T15:52:48.000Z","msg":"講漏 個班細路係睇落似高小以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/surprise_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"772e3958633a6a303c70ce0d689990df36f17190","tid":508822,"uid":56240,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T